steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"48kj5","text":"Set slide properly on the microscope and set new reference point","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7o598","text":"Click on Probes → Optical Fractionator Workflow → Start a new subject  →","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"col8g","text":"Enter cut thickness (5 µm (cut with microtome, 20 µm or 30 µm (cut with cryostat))","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"cfoov","text":"Enter interval according to the thickness: 17 if 5 µm, 6 if 20 µm or 4 if µm) ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"evp0","text":"In Manually enter the average mounted thickness enter the corresponding one","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"7ubmt","text":"In Define the Counting frame enter 50 x 50 µm","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9uk4o","text":"Enter 100x75 µm (if cut thickness is 5 µm) or 125x100 (if 20 µm or 30 µm)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"f6jf7","text":"In Optical Disector Height enter 5 µm, 20 µm or 30 µm ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3du4d","text":"Select a number of markers according to the desired cell types ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3bolt","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"cv1be","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":13,"offset":0,"style":"bold"}],"key":"415pu","text":"IMPORTANT 1: Count only the cells with visible nucleus within the square","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":13,"offset":0,"style":"bold"},{"length":4,"offset":136,"style":"bold"}],"key":"cvva5","text":"IMPORTANT 2: If a cell touches a line of the counting frame: if it touches the green line, count the cell; if it touches a red line, do not count it.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"d2j5v","text":"Count every defined region from every set section ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
